Most people don't really care. Even the majority of Green organisations have nothing to say on the matter. Green Peace for example is against nuclear power plants but never speaks up on spaceflight applications. Very few groups are silly enough to make an issue out of it and GN is the largest. Our site recieves more hits than theirs does and they have been around for decades. <br>
<br>
